## Full Version (Sponsor Access)

The full version of this project, including:
- Core generator code (karaoke_alignment_generator.py)
- Mobile generator code (karaoke_mobile_generator.py)
- Additional 50+ story templates
- Batch processing tools (50-100 videos per day)
- Advanced features and configurations
- Commercial use rights

is proprietary software and requires sponsorship to access.

### Sponsorship Terms

1. Personal Use License (Silver/Gold Tier):
   - Granted to individual sponsors
   - For personal and educational use only
   - Cannot be redistributed or used commercially
   - Valid for the lifetime of the sponsor

2. Commercial Use License (Diamond Tier):
   - Granted to diamond tier sponsors
   - Allows commercial use and distribution
   - Includes technical support
   - Valid for the lifetime of the sponsor

